<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181039>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Flagellotrema convolutum Ozaki, 1936 from Prionurus scalprum, presumably from Japan. Holotype. Scale bar = 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181039/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181040>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Flagellotrema convolutum Ozaki, 1936 from Prionurus scalprum, presumably from Japan. Detail of male terminal genitalia; composite sketch based on paratypes (sections). Scale bar = 250 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181040/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

